                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "Kate was a great TA/Professor, always gave good feedback to improve your essays before you turned them in and would always respond to emails and questions quickly. There were a lot of readings towards the beginning of the semester, but tapered off towards the end. Super understanding of everything and flexible based on your circumstances.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
